Third-party attributions
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This product includes design and implementation patterns adapted from the
Android Open Source Project (AOSP) Launcher3, licensed under the
Apache License, Version 2.0:

    https://android.googlesource.com/platform/packages/apps/Launcher3/
    Copyright (C) The Android Open Source Project

Launcher3 is a View-system application; the patterns below were re-implemented
from scratch in Jetpack Compose for this project (the model was adapted, not
the code copied verbatim):

  - the drag layer / drag controller model (cross-surface icon drag between
    the workspace, dock and app drawer);
  - live drop feedback and drop targets;
  - folders (drop icon-on-icon), notification dots, and pinned deep shortcuts.

This project does not include source code from Lawnchair (GPL-3.0); only
high-level concepts were studied from it.
